{"tid":681296,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人好似我咁用 optimization 管理自己個 portfolio","createTime":"2018-05-28T02:18:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T13:51:17.000Z","uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e90b4653c304c0592c4afc0fd09c505ef5407bd9","tid":681296,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T02:18:27.000Z","msg":"首先估算幾樣資產一年後既價格，訂一個 risk-free rate<br />\n然後 maximize log(expected value of portfolio) [i.e. Kelly criteria]<br />\n<br />\n會發現有兩個 matrix 要估算<br />\n用3年價格計嗰兩個 matrix 然後 take average <br />\n計 optimal portfolio<br />\n<br />\n然後睇下手上有幾多 cash<br />\nsolve 第二個 optimization problem<br />\n睇下點樣買賣最接近 optimal portfolio<br />\n而可以淨番一定量既錢再做買賣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"766d350951b51fc90a58e2246d126f3339237db6","tid":681296,"uid":66701,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:35:50.000Z","msg":"留名學習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你呢種算係價值估算?"},{"pid":"b4cecb8f296718328a1184f309c717c5d3bc5724","tid":681296,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"766d350951b51fc90a58e2246d126f3339237db6","tid":681296,"uid":66701,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:35:50.000Z","msg":"留名學習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你呢種算係價值估算?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:42:26.000Z","msg":"唔係 係風險管理"},{"pid":"6c2109210d51476bf0098c578deb83b19f4a711a","tid":681296,"uid":68118,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:51:42.000Z","msg":"計sd er cov果d？"},{"pid":"37098c31d916297471eefec4677aa45f34a254d7","tid":681296,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6c2109210d51476bf0098c578deb83b19f4a711a","tid":681296,"uid":68118,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:51:42.000Z","msg":"計sd er cov果d？"},"citedBy":0,"